1. *Veruj* mi, neće biti lako. (Believe me, it won't be easy.)
2. To je veoma teško *verovati*, ali je istinito. (It's very hard to believe, but it's true.)
3. Oni su *verovali* da će uspeti. (They believed they would succeed.)
4. Oni su *verovali* da će njihovo preduzeće biti uspešno. (They believed that their company would be successful.)
5. *Veruje* se da će biti još problema. (It is believed that there will be more problems.)
6. Oni su *verovali* u sebe. (They believed in themselves.)
7. Oni su *verovali* da su veoma uspešni. (They believed that they were very successful.)